<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283610>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Nothacrobeles abolafiai sp. n. (LM, female). A: Neck. B: Lip region (I: primary axil, II: secondary axil, 1 – 5: labial tines). C: Reproductive system. D: Lateral field. E: Posterior end (arrow indicates phasmid)." ;
